<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE SECOND COMING OF CHRIST</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiun Moneipa mel kipahum chun,
 Kawl kimvela A mite;
 A hun sapkhawm tieng,
 I chung thangvan mei kaihna a khun;
 Sapna aw gi lopi takin,
 &quot;Tho un! tho un, mithiengthote;
 Kumsawt taikhuo a vak tai&quot; ti'n,
 Ipmu hun phawng halh ta'n a.

[V2]
 &quot;Kiging unla, paucham zingun,
 Gitlohna a hunglien, thepna tui kinawk a sang ie;
 Muonna, muonna ti a I um laitak un,
 Manthaina hungtung ina.

[V3]
 2. Zie ni lopi chu a hung tun tieng leh,
 Kahna leh lungngaihna'n;
 Khawvel hung dim tan a,
 Hehpihna aw nem ngainuom lote;
 Hung halh untin lung kisikin,
 &quot;Lalpa! Lalpa! ti'n sam un au;
 Zie ni lopi lauhum chuh,
 Kahna'n hun mang zo tan au.

[V4]
 3. Sun lai ahim, khawvak kuon ahim a,
 Sapna aw lauhum chuh;
 A hung gittieng chu leh,
 Mi thiengtho than thim nuoia umte,
 Lopina tawh hung tho untin;
 Thi leh hingte'n mel danglam pu'n,
 I chung thangvan zawl nuom a khun,
 Chung kawlva bang leng tan au.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>150</hymn_number>
<author>Sawngkhawkhai</author>
</song>